{"tid":1462614,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"核彈都唔割只係一句口號?定係有人覺得用核彈後只係好少事","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:16:01.000Z","uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"332e3a83b2e6ec397e7abdf00da1b5fc72fb2e77","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"我明白有人覺得今日機場阻到旅客係做錯左,錯埋右<br />\n但係有咩必要講到咁嚴重,對比用核彈簡直係九毛一毛,真係完全不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當有痴線佬真係用核彈<br />\n咩野阻人返工<br />\n咩阻住旅客<br />\n咩野失民意<br />\n都唔講住<br />\n自己友未死哂都會因為輻射問題受到影響<br />\n咁嘅情況大家都話唔會割<br />\n唔好因為啲5毛帶風向就屌哂鬼咁啦<br />\n唔想見到啲人阻旅客出境解決方法好簡單 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日1百萬人出機場咪得</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe438aeb73ea65ef0d716da8d9260991472885bd","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"513299327c01505da633fbd5b421c5c168912f40","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"fd9d8d84b84e5b898a84826c1ecffb00695838b3","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"988e484addb8f38aaa466331970f54b7a3350464","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8b49ff40df8bd2b1fc726f8078f244902cd6040c","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"a0b4a1b9b8ca18021048b01f13a9c989a536e98e","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:59.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"e65ad3cf4284b1ea7f3ec72d901a4d149504a332","tid":1462614,"uid":270917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:09.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c5ed20086408221ff9efdd231bc6ea